gw.api.profiler

Class AggregatedQuerySummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.profiler.AggregatedQuerySummary
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArgsAggregatedQuerySummary, GloballyAggregatedQuerySummary, StackAggregatedQuerySummary

    public class AggregatedQuerySummary
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates a collection of QuerySummary objects, all of which have the same SQL query string. In addition to the query string and the underlying QuerySummary objects, this object also keeps track of the total execution counts and elapsed execution times of its contained queries.
    Author:
    cgross
